chips.description: Chips, only one line of content is allowed. If the content exceeds the width, the content will be automatically intercepted
chips.description_zh: 筹码，只允许一行内容。如果内容超过宽度，内容将被自动拦截

events.name: onTagClick
events.description: Click the bottom label to trigger, and it will only take effect when the label 'type' is' link '
events.description_zh: 点击底部标签触发，只有当标签'type'为'link'

events.name: onLinkClick
events.description: Clicking the link triggers an event that intercepts the href jump to the A tag
events.description_zh: 单击该链接会触发一个事件，该事件会拦截到 A 标记的 href 跳转
